todo for shell unit test

----
create directory for every test
merge log directory in this directory
example: test filename is test_foo.sh
dirname is test_foo.sh.dir
inside is directory workdir and files stdout, stderr and exitstatus
workdir is pwd of test process
stdout, stderr and exitstatus contains the stdout, stderr and exitstatus

----
create working directory for shut
this directory will contain the test directories
and logfile of entire stdout of shut
and text files listing failed and passed tests

----
capture stdout and stderr separately

----
recognize more than one pattern argument
shut pat1 pat2
